headline: Senators Call for DOJ Probe of X’s Advertiser Pressure Campaign
summary: Five Democratic senators have asked the Justice Department to investigate whether Elon Musk is leveraging his influence in the Trump administration to bully advertisers into returning to X.

headline: Senators ask DOJ to investigate whether Elon Musk is using his insider status in the Trump administration to pressure advertisers back to X
summary: Five Democratic senators said they’re concerned X is using Musk’s influential role to “extract revenue from advertisers,” the Wall Street Journal reported after viewing the letter sent to Attorney General Pam Bondi.
